{"tid":361210,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 一人一個分肥婆定大肚婆嘅方法","createTime":"2017-08-16T02:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T03:52:08.000Z","uid":96878,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af4ed8a527a8b896d856d274c6d8a7bd6f4b882d","tid":361210,"uid":96878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"有一次撘地鐵坐坐下見有個疑似大肚婆嘅物體上車 企正係小弟前面 我見我下兩個站就落 咪諗住扮下好心讓座俾佢 呢次係我第一次咁好心讓座 平時一定扮訓玩電話 扮睇唔到就算<br />\n<br />\n我: 讓你坐丫 大肚婆又要企又要逼好辛苦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢果下呆左呆 然後變哂臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇坐到<br />\n我發覺唔對路 重新再望到似佢個身 我屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢係一個死肥婆 唔係大肚婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個樣當堂變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我紅都臉哂 明明仲有兩個站先落車 見咁啱開左門就唔理三七廿一即將衝落車 果刻我覺得自己仲柒過關家姐<br />\n<br />\n從此以後 我就唔敢再讓座俾大肚婆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc4b59062cbed5b46acdd5bacd22f844d66ba72","tid":361210,"uid":96878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一次撘地鐵坐坐下見有個疑似大肚婆嘅物體上車 企正係小弟前面 我見我下兩個站就落 咪諗住扮下好心讓座俾佢 呢次係我第一次咁好心讓座 平時一定扮訓玩電話 扮睇唔到就算<br />\n<br />\n我: 讓你坐丫 大肚婆又要企又要逼好辛苦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢果下呆左呆 然後變哂臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇坐到<br />\n我發覺唔對路 重新再望<span style=\"color: red;\">多次</span>佢個身 我屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢係一個死肥婆 唔係大肚婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個樣當堂變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我紅都臉哂 明明仲有兩個站先落車 見咁啱開左門就唔理三七廿一即將衝落車 果刻我覺得自己仲柒過關家姐<br />\n<br />\n從此以後 我就唔敢再讓座俾大肚婆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"609ccd0b813c289953604f9fa61d10da48bfd211","tid":361210,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:23:27.000Z","msg":"你彈番句鬼知你肥定大肚<br />\n全車都笑到碌地啦"},{"pid":"9a73d8cfeff22a4288cf72d28e0119e2030d2c6d","tid":361210,"uid":23170,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過嗰個鬼婆，佢仲笑住咁同我講，no no no, i'm not pregnant, just fat, 叫我坐返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4249089e4b7abba482aed0943785e5df7f0a53d8","tid":361210,"uid":50845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:28:03.000Z","msg":"點解要識分？<br />\n理得佢肥定大肚 唔坐關座咪得"},{"pid":"fd29009749932bcd12ae73673d8a4671c154bc55","tid":361210,"uid":13174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T02:32:14.000Z","msg":"聞下佢個身<br />\n肥婆一定有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\